---
title: Teriyaki Beef with Shanghai Bok Choy and Carrots
description: A stir-fry is the perfect, speedy weeknight dinner to whip up after a long day. This one is jam-packed with vegetables that will nourish and satisfy. The gingery beef is the best bit; it’s marinated in a yummy sauce that will leave you weak at the knees.
